## Quickstart

```bash
docker compose up -d
docker compose logs -f ollama-pull   # wait for the model to be pulled
```

Open `http://localhost` — register an admin account, create a knowledge base, and upload docs.

## Add MCP tool

```bash
perfectrag add mcp tavily --project .
# then restart ragflow to reload the config
docker compose restart ragflow
```

## Add skill

```bash
perfectrag add skill legal-rag --project .
```

Skills are mounted into `/ragflow/skills` (read-only).

